      "code": "# Try contains some part\nparts = [\"إنما بعثت\", \"لأتمم مكارم\", \"مكارم الأخلاق\", \"بعثت لاتمم\"]\nnorm_parts = [normalize(p) for p in parts]\nhits=[]\nfor rec in hadith:\n    text = rec.get('hadithTxt') or rec.get('Matn') or ''\n    ntext = normalize(text)\n    if all(p in ntext for p in norm_parts[:1]): # first part\n        if any(p in ntext for p in norm_parts[1:]):\n            hits.append(text)\nlen(hits)",
